銷 5Cs？請詳述並舉例說明之。（25 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:27:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "45eb14745af2", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112070", "c": "131", "s": "0311", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "公共管理", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試警察人員考試、一般警察人員考試、國家安全情報人員考試、交通事業鐵路人員考試、退除役軍人轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "retired", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('retired-7fec267e-moex-00130', 'retired-7fec267e', 'retired-7fec267e-moex-112-5a8e61f1', 'sub-retired-7fec267e-07', NULL, 'essay', '現代的公共管理行為常牽涉到多重行動者，學者將多重行動者的關係稱
